## References

* [N. Bourbaki, *Lie groups and {L}ie algebras. {C}hapters 1--3*][bourbaki1975]
-- extensions are chapter 1 section 7, cohomology is Exercises section 3 (p116, near end of book)


## Tags

lie ring, lie algebra, central extension
-/

